events.name: World Hopping (ALX45)
events.marketing:
Who: ALX45

A world hopping event where we do about 15 minutes in between world to explore and have fun. This allows us to do two things! For *LPD MEMBERS*, this allows us to find new worlds to patrol instead of the old basic great pug, kmart, etc. For *NON LPD MEMBERS*, this allows them to become more interactive within the LPD, find cool worlds, and see the LPD community outside of the "find you, arrest you" mentality.
